  "text": "Skip to content\nHome\nATMP-Courier\nATMP-Core\nCustomer Order\nDriver Access\nLeadership\nPress\nContact Us\nSaber Tech Launches Cutting-Edge Platform to Transform Last-Mile Delivery\n\nSaber Tech today announced the beta launch of its Last-Mile Courier Platform, a production-ready system the company operates to power real-world delivery execution and visibility. This milestone marks Saber Tech’s first fully deployable platform, now running live across the United States and Canada.\n\nThe beta focuses exclusively on last-mile courier operations, delivering reliable dispatch coordination, real-time tracking, exception handling, and operational visibility across local and regional networks. It is purpose-built to ensure on-time, transparent, and professional delivery execution, without attempting to serve as a full supply chain or transportation management system.\n\nBy directly operating the platform, Saber Tech maintains complete control over performance, reliability, and day-to-day operations, allowing the team to refine and optimize the system in real-world conditions.\n\nWhile the company envisions a broader logistics ecosystem, this beta prioritizes stability and consistent last-mile performance, laying the foundation for scalable, dependable delivery solutions.\n\nWith this beta launch, Saber Tech solidifies its reputation as an operator-first technology company, deploying systems only when they are proven ready for real-world operations. Each release is deliberately scoped to ensure fully deployable, production-ready performance, with additional platform functionality introduced only when it meets the same rigorous operational standards.\nMedia Contact\n\nVal Olson\nChief Public Relations Officer\nSaber Tech\nEmail: volson@sabertechlogistics.com\n\nTrusted Solutions, Every Mile\nTrust Saber Tech to handle every delivery with expertise and operational excellence.\nFacebook\n \nInstagram\nQuick Links\nATMP-Courier\nATMP-Core\nCustomer Order\nDriver Access\nLeadership\nPress\nContact\nSupport\nAbout\nCustomer Order Portal\nDriver App\nSaber Tech © 2026 • Built on ATMP-core • Owner and operator centric logistics platform.\nPrivacy Policy\nTerms & Conditions\nTranslate »",
